abstract: Data will include the Consumer Price Index for September, and company reports from Citigroup and General Electric.
snippet: Data will include the Consumer Price Index for September, and company reports from Citigroup and General Electric.
lead_paragraph: ECONOMIC REPORTS Data will include industrial production and capacity use for September (Monday); the Producer Price Index for September (Tuesday); the Consumer Price Index for September, housing starts for September and the Federal Reserve beige book (Wednesday); existing-home sales for September, Philadelphia Fed manufacturing index for October and leading economic indicators for September (Thursday).

headline.main: Economic Reports for the Week Ahead

abstract: At a conference, Jeffrey R. Immelt, the chief executive of General Electric, did not despair over stagnant domestic growth and increased competition from China and other foreign producers.
